{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60001","type":"text","x":-1100,"y":-700,"width":2200,"height":120,"text":"# LLM Wiki Methodology\n\nUniversal LLM knowledge base construction pattern · Markdown + Obsidian · Human-AI collaboration"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60100","type":"group","x":-1100,"y":-540,"width":700,"height":580,"label":"Three-Layer Architecture","color":"6"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60101","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":-480,"width":620,"height":140,"color":"6","text":"### Raw Sources\n\nYour curated source docs · Articles / papers / data\n\n*Immutable · LLM read-only*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60102","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":-300,"width":620,"height":160,"color":"4","text":"### Wiki Layer — LLM-generated Markdown\n\nSummaries / Entity pages / Concept pages / Comparisons\n\n*LLM fully owns · You read-only*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60103","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":-100,"width":620,"height":140,"color":"2","text":"### Schema Layer — CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md\n\nConventions / Structure / Workflow\n\n*You and LLM co-evolve*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60200","type":"group","x":-360,"y":-540,"width":720,"height":580,"label":"Three Core Operations","color":"6"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60201","type":"text","x":-320,"y":-480,"width":640,"height":160,"color":"6","text":"### ● Ingest\n\nFeed source docs → LLM reads / discusses / writes summaries / updates index\n\n*One source may touch 10–15 Wiki pages*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60202","type":"text","x":-320,"y":-300,"width":640,"height":160,"color":"4","text":"### ● Query\n\nAsk the Wiki → Search / synthesize / cite\n\n*Good answers get archived back to the Wiki as new pages*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60203","type":"text","x":-320,"y":-100,"width":640,"height":140,"color":"2","text":"### ● Lint — Maintenance\n\nRegular health checks: conflicts / outdated / orphan pages / broken links\n\n*LLM suggests new questions and new sources*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60300","type":"group","x":400,"y":-540,"width":700,"height":280,"label":"Index & Log","color":"4"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60301","type":"text","x":440,"y":-480,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"4","text":"### index.md\n\nContent navigation\n\nTable of contents for all pages\n\n*LLM reads index first, then reviews pages*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60302","type":"text","x":760,"y":-480,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"2","text":"### log.md\n\nTime navigation\n\nAppend-only operation history\n\n`## [Date] Type | Title`"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60400","type":"group","x":400,"y":-240,"width":700,"height":280,"label":"Role Division","color":"3"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60401","type":"text","x":440,"y":-180,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"6","text":"### You — Human\n\nCurate sources\n\nAsk questions\n\nGuide direction"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60402","type":"text","x":760,"y":-180,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"5","text":"### LLM — AI\n\nSummarize / Cross-reference\n\nArchive\n\nMaintain consistency"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60500","type":"group","x":-1100,"y":100,"width":1460,"height":540,"label":"Ingest Flow","color":"6"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60501","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":180,"width":240,"height":100,"color":"2","text":"**New Source Doc**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60502","type":"text","x":-780,"y":180,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"6","text":"**LLM Reads & Analyzes**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60503","type":"text","x":-460,"y":180,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"5","text":"**Discuss Key Points with You**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60504","type":"text","x":-140,"y":180,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"4","text":"**Update Wiki**\n\nWrite summaries + update entity pages"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60511","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":380,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"4","text":"**Summary Page**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60512","type":"text","x":-760,"y":380,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"4","text":"**Entity Pages × N**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60513","type":"text","x":-460,"y":380,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"4","text":"**Concept Page**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60514","type":"text","x":-160,"y":380,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"2","text":"**Update index**"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60520","type":"text","x":-1060,"y":520,"width":1380,"height":60,"text":"*One source document may touch 10–15 Wiki pages*"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60600","type":"group","x":400,"y":100,"width":1280,"height":540,"label":"Use Cases","color":"4"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60601","type":"text","x":440,"y":180,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"6","text":"### Personal Growth\n\nJournals / health / psychology"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60602","type":"text","x":740,"y":180,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"4","text":"### Deep Research\n\nPapers / reports / presentations"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60603","type":"text","x":1040,"y":180,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"5","text":"### Reading Companion\n\nPeople / themes / plot pages"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60604","type":"text","x":1340,"y":180,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"2","text":"### Team Knowledge Base\n\nSlack / meetings / docs"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60605","type":"text","x":440,"y":360,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"1","text":"### Competitive Analysis\n\nDue diligence / comparison"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60606","type":"text","x":740,"y":360,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"#e879c4","text":"### Travel Planning\n\nItinerary / spots / tips"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60607","type":"text","x":1040,"y":360,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"3","text":"### Course Notes\n\nBuild knowledge system"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60608","type":"text","x":1340,"y":360,"width":280,"height":140,"color":"3","text":"### Interest Deep-Dive\n\nAny knowledge accumulation"},
		{"id":"a1b2c3d4e5f60700","type":"text","x":-1100,"y":700,"width":2780,"height":220,"color":"3","text":"## Core Insight\n\nThe bottleneck of maintaining a knowledge base is **not reading or thinking** — it is **bookkeeping**: updating citations, maintaining consistency, flagging contradictions.\n\nHumans abandon wikis because maintenance burden grows faster than value. **LLMs never tire, never forget, can touch 15 files at once. Maintenance cost approaches zero.**"}
	],
